org.apache.flink.api.java.record.operators

Class GenericDataSink

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.api.common.operators.Operator<Nothing>
      • org.apache.flink.api.common.operators.base.GenericDataSinkBase<Record>
        • org.apache.flink.api.java.record.operators.GenericDataSink
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Visitable<Operator<?>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HadoopDataSink

    public class GenericDataSink
extends GenericDataSinkBase<Record>
    Operator for nodes that act as data sinks, storing the data they receive. The way the data is stored is handled by the OutputFormat.
